➜酷黑姿态高尔夫，迎娶最美新娘，这是情人节最好的礼物
http://www.sohu.com/a/373259041_163713	27428
<p class="ql-align-justify">第一眼，我就知道那是大众；但是第一眼，我压根认不出那是大众哪款车。Volkswagen在中国，就是爱展现这种如此“独特”的德味。<strong>如果，只能选一台大众留下，我想得票最高的，会是它，高尔夫。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/3fe1ca61844d452eb6b146fa2e3ee174.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/640dee90625b43ccae3534c04c4f938f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这次，和往常不同，车主余老师没有投稿到我们邮箱，我也没对车主进行采访，而是在微信上，<strong>车主像讲故事一样，和我分享着他那不一般的改装路。</strong>“下面，这是我最开始的小白时期。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/0bdf842b1b1b448f84e0a748fa48c193.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“我本身是个美术老师，所以<strong>审美观都比较张扬</strong>。后来为了吸引眼球，还改了橙色，装了一车的假货，也就是所谓人见人恶的<strong>汽配风</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/547393538ae44bed9af1a64c464c4525.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“后来被网上的人说教了，于是换上了我的第一套<strong>祖国轮毂</strong>，脸圈FF74。然后，更加杀马特的是，我<strong>还贴上了轮胎字</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/ce695f7ed9944b85a9625ea29f73e839.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“通过查资料看案例，频繁的不耻下问，最后才深<strong>刻认识到了，什么是真正意义上的改装车</strong>。然后，贴上电光黑改色膜，走上了黑武士这条路。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/e628af31ed8f409fa1dffa8a01b682c9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/74f8c276d2b4450b9315fc6b61bb081e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“改成了<strong>7代GTI的套件</strong>，还装了当时非常火的时宇大灯，选了<strong>红色双U恶魔眼</strong>，觉得<strong>黑红</strong>很配。然后，找朋友拍了第一组的套图。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/e1aef358bf3746c588d0cc3ac22f045d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/ba31970fe3c947f1938978c0032e1dd4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/b7374bdb67ec4fd59b9c475cd1114246.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“毕竟，我的<strong>发动机只是1.4T</strong>，即使<strong>刷了1阶</strong>，动力也好不到哪里去。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/94405c4427524fd08b903a51a6c55aa9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“所以，<strong>还是决定走姿态</strong>的路线，也其实深深中毒低趴已久。于是乎跑去了合肥朋友的改装店里，<strong>装了一套Maso</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/002e7b4cda2548eebb5f71c96b6c6108.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/bfbdfd3b93c640dba1ad8057b731c3cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/168745519ac3462aa0d6213745dd04a6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/8060d9e654114831ad8373690ca7b970.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/d60d2af140d04eebb560d7c367f3c130.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“<strong>后备箱的造型，也都是自己的设计</strong>。当时迷上了Star Wars，所以后备箱，连同车内的一些小点缀，都DIY成了自己喜欢的星球大战风格！”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/1febc1c048404366b038ac4733d6fc51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/e7ee89fee6634c39af2d80f8ba801b9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/e32f5de76ed548e686b442b6405a58ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“返璞归真，慢慢又开始喜欢<strong>上了素车的改装</strong>。也因为这样，换上了第二套轮毂，金色的<strong>rotiform</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/422aff3e52e7437387604d4d6699990d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/b4ebfe2eceac44a0a72a58bd8097ba22.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/fcfefa723bd7410fb886afefd3f46e4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/fa15d288fe394b05aab5dbf9867d0b7a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“后备箱的造型，<strong>依然坚持走自己的路线</strong>，一直在换。也很欣慰，我的改装得到了不少车友的喜欢，也就加入了玩大众的组织，跟着车友们，还参加了一些车展。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/b0f19dba8ff549fa95f87d7089578abc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/7781099fa4034e83996e82cdeebc226f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/d18cb3af67804213a05a8e816541cecf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“再下一步，就是<strong>被宽体的魅力洗脑</strong>了，最终说服了自己，狠下心去割了叶子板，做了CMST的宽体。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/1376a24a09ba4972ab255073c1ef62c6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/bcb4852d768e4626b3feb987ab2034aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“继续就是细节的处理，<strong>又换了一套轮毂，真正的脸圈FF76</strong>。把自己一路坚持的黑武士，彻彻底底的<strong>进行全面黑化</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/9963011e9049479fb8208cc38dde5d55.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/5f56b21ce6d24160b911c2a9a07adcf9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“像中网、机盖、泄压阀、进气、排气、尾翼.. 基本能改的都改了！乱七八槽加上弯路，有15万上下了。这么多冤枉钱，也<strong>全车正品了，怎么感觉就是没出来</strong>？我还是归咎于轮毂，所以，<strong>又换了套抛边的rotiform</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/e957db8f164a413ba0a82781066e75c0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/309df526a0124d2585284277e3595cf9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/ab4f718c63054fc588fd49cf1f36ccf8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/a91aac7b0fc940879c4902d27ca4cf9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“哈哈，后来还<strong>背上了个帅帅的小书包</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/da6b61efd1a34ab5825d2df640e33dd2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/64778e3601fe41299fccdf48daa01fd2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/7c47456eef8e4106b005815d138d458b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“到这，感觉外观弄得差不多了，于是打起了内饰的主意。其实我<strong>个人挺钟情于日本文化的</strong>，所以衍生出了一个奇怪的想法，搞个<strong>外德内日</strong>会怎样呢。于是，内饰就变成了下面这个样，哈哈 ~ ”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/c576622e99a74163adcc37d9983c516e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/1a9fadaf5b9a48d6b73c1870cb95bf93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/55afc0d3db62414c9273d9566d2e3f8a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/ce859b030c1a40489e52e96e3340b98d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">“说好的不弄外观，但还是没憋住啦。<strong>抵挡不住诱惑，换了套SD三片锻造的圈</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/242b0686f6ad482c8d90c2fbf189542b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/bae3c763fe2846b4b27c948f0f72d9ea.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/5d0c109157114880b9859098a7b2a9a5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/4a6c09a0b602434fa376a6e581686e93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“最开心的，还是<strong>认识到了一群非常有爱的车友</strong>。一起改，一起玩，一起跑，还能一起帅，<strong>各种的满足</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/0da28e84fdd94b8cad96408ce3dc19af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/afe6c702a98a4ccbbd142d85d037213e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/0ac0341a6b3844fc8b688bc87ab3296c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/e360e8021c3e43ef9eb4adf2423b47a2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“平时我有玩抖音的习惯，爱发自己的车，随着时间积累，<strong>自己在抖音上也有了很多志同道合的粉丝</strong>。”</p>
<p>“而这台高尔夫，也陪着我，<strong>走进了婚姻的殿堂</strong>。这是幸福的，<strong>我最爱的车，和我最爱的女人</strong>，都在我身边了。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/5781bb1c5d7f4e508ed69adc4dbee2ec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/576f946824534ca0a2af81a66bee951e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/38a23cf75474437e86c9ca47f22a34bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/97c033cbe2b740a8b24b3f030a137600.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“最后，就认真地洗个车吧，爱车的人，应该都会很享受。<strong>干干净净的她</strong>，是真的，<strong>真的很美</strong>。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/9768a6c682024ba394f048fc7ea3f17e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/ffc663372bdd44c78555bbbfb9053b1d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/9b194826e73a4a1b911e8ddb3dee1377.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/5cb4a482b39248b6b8cebecdf69212a3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>我是在微信里，看完车主整个改装故事的，有羡慕，有触动，有感慨。<strong>改装是深坑，但，几乎所有车主的答案都是，无悔入坑，</strong>还收获了一大群车友、兄弟。这种坑，不值得跳么？</p>
<p>已经进坑的、正准备跳的、还有那些已经不想出来了的，<strong>留言区，报个到</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200215/5434a2b1e959455089c974be4cd85c73.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
